{"tid":1649356,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"美國《反抵制法》","createTime":"2019-10-12T15:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T17:25:16.000Z","uid":134993,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"20448c0190c4a9145a1f92b6eb6d973b5ab20d5b","tid":1649356,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:26:12.000Z","msg":"NBA事件出現了逆轉。中共試圖給事件降溫，黨媒下令記者不得繼續炒作，以免後果失控。但美國政界民間開始聚焦中共霸凌，並提出以法律對抗中共對美國企業施加政治影響力。<br />\n<br />\n美國NBA火箭隊總經理莫雷發推特撐香港，惹怒中共。不過在大陸官方民間一片「抵制NBA」的喧囂聲中，今年首場「NBA中國大陸賽」10號照常在上海舉行。當天場內滿座，球迷不時為球星歡呼喝采，沒有爆發激烈抗議場面。<br />\n<br />\n但美國政界民間開始聚焦中共霸凌。魯比奧參議員提出，按照美國《反抵制法》，那些在美國上市、或在美國有分支機構的中國企業，不得參與「美國未曾參與的制裁或抵制」，否則可能被取消稅務優惠，或被課以罰款等。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴、騰訊、京東符合上述條件，但它們都參與了「抵制NBA」的行動。魯比奧議員點名這幾家公司，並要求川普政府嚴格執法。"},{"pid":"0291ebb5b91bc9fc2bf7f39220689d68306d4563","tid":1649356,"uid":80277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FpwbJYZ.jpeg&h=fea4b22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/3DeFV2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2F3DeFV2.jpeg&h=11fde298&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d127a64cace97da41c82e4e43f65a721a7283548","tid":1649356,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9b9499da05b37778e000841b5457737e98a27c","tid":1649356,"uid":152222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:31:15.000Z","msg":"爽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d026b9a347d2b58b97455a6253ecdf129738be8","tid":1649356,"uid":286670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":